# LOCAL DEV / E2E ONLY — never loaded by `next build` on Vercel (NODE_ENV=production).
# Applied by `npm run dev` via scripts/run-dev.mjs and by Playwright via scripts/load-app-env.mjs.
# Production deploys must set hosted values in the hosting dashboard; see ENV.md.
# Keys only work against the Supabase CLI stack on 127.0.0.1:54321 (see `supabase status -o env`).
# Auth emails are captured by Mailpit — nothing is sent externally.

